For building the code: pip download -d ./deps -r requirements.txt --only-binary=:all: --platform manylinux2014_x86_64
For creating the topics if for whatever reason the Pulsar brokers need to be replaced

1. Create the tenant
bin/pulsar-admin tenants create apache


2. Create the namespaces
bin/pulsar-admin namespaces create apache/pulsar

3. Create the source topic
bin/pulsar-admin topics create-partitioned-topic apache/pulsar/wiki-topic -p 3

4. Set retention on namespaces

bin/pulsar-admin functions create --function-config-file=/mnt/c/Users/Anna/CodeProjects/pulsar-producer/create-config.yaml --cpu=0.2 --ram=400000000